title: FortiSwitch: Chassis Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/fortinet
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors chassis temperature sensors of Fortinet FortiSwitch devices
 via the ENTITY-SENSOR-MIB. Sensors are discovered dynamically and named
 from the ENTITY-MIB physical name (e.g. Sensor1, Board Temp (1)).
 SFP/DOM optical temperature sensors are excluded.

 The check uses Checkmk's standard temperature framework, so levels,
 trend computation and unit display are configured via the built-in
 "Temperature" ruleset (default 60/70 degrees C).

item:
 The sensor name from the ENTITY-MIB.

discovery:
 One service is created per chassis temperature sensor with a value.
